                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>before last; a very large assemblage was<lb/> present, &amp; the\n                                        profit at present estimated<lb/> will be about $1500; really\n                                        the Ball was<lb/> an honour to the Jews here, and creditable\n                                        to<lb/> the managers; everything passed of to the<lb/>\n                                        satisfaction of all present; one unusual<lb/> feature of the\n                                        Ball was the large<lb/> number of Ladies, which numbered\n                                        to<lb/> about 200. It is due to our Jewish po-<lb/>-pulation\n                                        to say, that a great number of our<lb/> persuasion are very\n                                        much respected as<lb/> first class &amp; prominent\n                                        citizens.</p>\n                              <p><persName>Mr. Cohen</persName> has been to see me &amp; told me\n                                        a<lb/> great deal of the China-Jews, but as he<lb/> has\n                                        given you already much Information<lb/> in that regard,\n                                        &amp; as he told me he would<lb/> write to you again by next\n                                        mail, it<lb/> would be fore me unnecessary to say\n                                        any-<lb/>-thing upon that subject. I think you<lb/> would\n                                        have done wise if you would have<lb/> advertised in your\n                                        Occident, that your<lb/> Books could be had by me. I am<lb/>\n                                        well acquainted with <persName>Mr. Chay\n                                        Emanuel</persName>,<lb/> &amp; he requests me to give his\n                                        Regards to you.<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Mrs &amp; Mr. Roggenburger</persName> wish kindly\n                                        to be<lb/> remembered to you. With my best wishes for<lb/>\n                                        your good Health &amp; Prosperity I remain yours Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Cauffman H. Meyer</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"The following is written sideways in the left margin\">The\n                                        enclosed Notice I have cut out from the “daily California\n                                        Chronicle”<lb/> all papers unite in speaking highly of the\n                                        Ball.</p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3k06xm56/canvas/p2"
                }
